"signal_description": "The SIGNAL query is calculating a percentage from the 'defaultview-290' table. It first counts the number of 'case_id' where there is at least one 'event_name' that equals 'DeliveryGoodsMovementOnTime' and has a value of 'Yes'. This count is then divided by the count of 'case_id' where there is at least one 'event_name' that is 'Create Outbound Delivery'. The result of this division is then multiplied by 100 to get the percentage. The purpose of this query is to find the percentage of cases where goods are delivered on time out of all outbound delivery cases."
